Name: AnotherQuizzGame
About the game: AnotherQuizzGame or ' AQG ' is a indie game, the main purpose is to answer multiple quizzes created or not by the community! So find many quizzes around many diverse and varied topics of the Culture of Videogames, cinema or a questionnaire on charcuterie ! You will have understood, here it is YOU ARE the creator! you will have at your disposal the mode 'Editor' which will allow you to create your own quiz and share them FOR FREE worldwide ! The quizzes have many parameters and are fully customizable! You will find : • Set lifes • Defind the question type : - True or False - Multiple Answer Questions - Text Answer • Defind the number of question and more ! Here, everything is important, every animation, every interface, every music... EVERYTHING MUST SHINE! EVERYTHING MUST BE BEAUTIFUL!
